# ==============================================================================
# TEMPLATE VARIABLES FILE
# ==============================================================================
# INSTRUCTIONS: 
# 1. Copy this file and rename it to 'terraform.tfvars'
# 2. Replace the dummy values below with your actual AWS details.
# 3. DO NOT commit the real 'terraform.tfvars' file to version control.
